        {
            "title": "伊朗拒絕美國停火提議 稱談判不合邏輯",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7vsPtL1T0bhwOtrhhdrpEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_4_M_1440048337.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據法爾斯通訊社週三援引知情人士消息,伊朗已拒絕美國的停火提議,稱在目前條件下停火和談判並不可行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該消息人士告訴法爾斯通訊社,伊朗不接受停火,並認為與美國的談判不合邏輯。儘管伊朗稱美國加大了爭取停火的努力,但仍遭到拒絕。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週二,以色列第12頻道報導稱,外交努力正在進行中,旨在建立美國與伊朗之間為期一個月的停火機制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《紐約時報》報導,美國向伊朗發送了一份包含15點內容的計劃,以結束中東戰爭。官員表示,該計劃是通過巴基斯坦轉交的,巴基斯坦軍隊總司令已成為兩國之間的關鍵仲介人。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ef7be301-95fa-3300-aa78-f289ebd08895-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價在該消息傳出後攀升,但自傳聞浮現以來仍處於較低水平,而股市則收窄漲幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E6%8F%90%E8%AD%B0-%E7%A8%B1%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF-134129432.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 22:05:27",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "MU、WDC、SNDK下跌:為何Google的TurboQuant令記憶體股震盪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9JNZKY6n10_bBMBp286eBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEB7R05V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 儘管科技板塊整體表現強勁,記憶體股週三仍然下跌。在Google推出TurboQuant這項可能降低AI系統記憶體需求的新壓縮演算法後,相關股價應聲下挫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SanDisk Corporation(NASDAQ:SNDK)下跌5.7%,美光科技(NASDAQ:MU)下跌3%,西部數據(NASDAQ:WDC)下跌4.7%,希捷科技(NASDAQ:STX)下跌4%。這些跌幅出現在納斯達克100指數上漲之際。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4bbafae1-a94f-3256-9e9b-ea8286815675-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Google推出了TurboQuant,這是一項旨在降低大型語言模型和向量搜尋引擎記憶體消耗的壓縮技術。該演算法解決了鍵值快取的瓶頸問題,鍵值快取用於儲存AI系統中經常存取的資訊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Google的公告,TurboQuant可以將鍵值快取壓縮至3位元,無需訓練或微調,同時保持模型準確性。在包括Gemma和Mistral在內的開源模型上進行的測試顯示,該技術實現了鍵值記憶體大小6倍的縮減。該演算法還在H100 GPU加速器上展現了比未量化鍵值高達8倍的效能提升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該技術透過兩個步驟運作:應用PolarQuant方法透過旋轉資料向量實現高品質壓縮,以及使用量化Johnson-Lindenstrauss演算法消除殘餘誤差。Google表示,傳統的向量量化方法在記憶體開銷中每個數字增加1至2個額外位元,部分抵消了壓縮優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TurboQuant將在ICLR 2026上發表,而PolarQuant計劃在AISTATS 2026上發表。Google在包括LongBench、Needle In A Haystack、ZeroSCROLLS、RULER和L-Eval在內的基準測試中測試了這些演算法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該技術的應用範圍超越了AI模型,還包括為大規模搜尋引擎提供動力的向量搜尋功能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">記憶體股今年迄今已大幅上漲,使其容易受到可能降低需求的發展影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/mu-wdc-sndk%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95google%E7%9A%84turboquant%E4%BB%A4%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1%E9%9C%87%E7%9B%AA-144945449.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 23:11:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
